00:22:16,279 --> 00:22:17,119
some kind of counter.

563
00:22:17,559 --> 00:22:19,559
7, 8, 5, 2, 3, 1

564
00:22:19,559 --> 00:22:20,180
whatever you need.

565
00:22:20,859 --> 00:22:22,740
Your receipt needs a number.

566
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:25,359
So, we set the number

567
00:22:26,079 --> 00:22:27,900
in transaction receipt setup.

568
00:22:29,250 --> 00:22:29,490
Clear?

569
00:22:30,859 --> 00:22:31,380
Guys?

570
00:22:34,299 --> 00:22:34,819
After that,

571
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:35,940
what happens is

572
00:22:35,940 --> 00:22:37,579
we go to our stage setup

573
00:22:37,579 --> 00:22:38,920
and at the stage

574
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,259
in which I have to collect

575
00:22:40,259 --> 00:22:43,359
I go to the stage

576
00:22:43,359 --> 00:22:44,500
and set it.

577
00:22:45,019 --> 00:22:46,460
Suppose, I need something at the first stage

578
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:48,279
I need another head at the second stage

579
00:22:48,279 --> 00:22:51,660
I need multiple heads at the same stage

580
00:22:51,660 --> 00:22:53,720
then that is also possible.

581
00:22:54,019 --> 00:22:54,880
Like we did in this

582
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,039
data required

583
00:22:56,039 --> 00:22:57,819
in registration

584
00:22:58,680 --> 00:22:59,440
transaction

585
00:23:01,519 --> 00:23:04,380
two heads are set together.

586
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,119
We can also do different things for different courses.

587
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:07,920
For example, in this course

588
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,380
we are only taking the visit fee

589
00:23:09,380 --> 00:23:10,700
and in this course we are taking both.

590
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,880
So, what will the system do?

591
00:23:13,059 --> 00:23:14,180
As soon as the child is approved

592
00:23:14,180 --> 00:23:15,119
after collecting the payment

593
00:23:15,119 --> 00:23:17,059
the token money will be adjusted

594
00:23:17,059 --> 00:23:19,880
and the rest of the fees will only be visible to you.

595
00:23:20,359 --> 00:23:25,039
Is it clear guys?

596
00:23:27,220 --> 00:23:27,599
Yes.

597
00:23:30,599 --> 00:23:33,079
This was all about your

598
00:23:33,839 --> 00:23:35,539
transaction and token money.

